headline: GCC $1.25+ Bn Catheter Market Growth Trends and Forecast to 2033 Featuring Abbott, Edwards Lifesciences, BD and Co, Boston Scientific, Medtronic, Johnson & Johnson, Stryker, Teleflex
summary: The GCC catheter market is projected to grow from USD 579.83 million in 2024 to USD 1.28 billion by 2033, with a CAGR of 9.21% from 2025 to 2033. This growth is driven by an increase in chronic diseases, surgical procedures, and advanced healthcare infrastructure across GCC countries. The demand for minimally invasive treatments and the aging population further bolster market expansion.
